{"tid":2093652,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"形容中央「管極少」港澳辦：人大可按情況再制訂新例","createTime":"2020-07-04T04:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T05:07:22.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f7541875b5bfb4cac94b4fc88ae95e8f94084d2c","tid":2093652,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/874p0/0x0/100/hd/9c3e7bd49cf06f971debac76a9686b50/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200704/_2020070411412238154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F874p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F9c3e7bd49cf06f971debac76a9686b50%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200704%2F_2020070411412238154.jpg&h=002ff904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧中華指，人大常委會未來可按香港實際情況，繼續制定相關法律及定罪量刑。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n港區國安法上月30日在本港落實。國務院港澳辦副主任鄧中華指，全國人大常委會未來可按香港實際情況，繼續制定相關法律及定罪量刑。<br />\n<br />\n鄧中華昨日接受中央電視台訪問時指，5月28日人大授權常委會制定港區國安法非一次性，未來人大常委會可按香港實際情況，繼續制定相關法律，以及就有關行為定罪量刑。<br />\n<br />\n他指，國安是港區國安法的法理依據和法理出發點，屬中央事權。但他認為，港區國安法只針對4種罪行，中央駐港機構也只會對這4種罪行進行管轄，形容中央「管極少」，大部分都交由特區相關機構管轄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/1107eb50176d65cb82d0e36840a8dc88/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200704/_2020070411352860483.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F1107eb50176d65cb82d0e36840a8dc88%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200704%2F_2020070411352860483.jpg&h=453b9a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄧中華指，人大常委會未來可按香港實際情況，繼續制定相關法律及定罪量刑。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1811410/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE-%E7%AE%A1%E6%A5%B5%E5%B0%91-%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E8%BE%A6-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%AF%E6%8C%89%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81%E5%86%8D%E5%88%B6%E8%A8%82%E6%96%B0%E4%BE%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1811410%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%